snippet.textDisplay:
There's one big problem with this song. 
Even though Ali Sethi did an excellent job at singing, it's still a REMAKE of an old song. All popular Coke Studio songs WITHOUT EXCEPTION are remakes of older melodies.

This shows a seriously dangerous trend for the Pakistani music industry and Coke Studio. It's that we've become incapable of PRODUCING and DIRECTING new melodies and songs and are just recycling older stuff. 
Cole Studio unfortunately has brought nothing new to the table for the last 3 seasons.
